\fBspar\fP is interpreted as the total integrated intensity
instead of the peak value of the object
.TPtotflux
\fBcrpix=\fP
Override/Set crpix (1,1,1) // ignored []  
.TP
\fBcrval=\fP
Override/Set crval (0,0,0) // ignored []  
.TP
\fBcdelt=\fP
Override/Set cdelt (1,1,1) // ignored []  
.TP
\fBseed=\fP
